keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here.
unmap h
unmap H
unmap j
unmap k
unmap J
unmap K
unmap l
unmap L
unmap F
unmap f

F nextFrame
map h goBack
" lowercase L here:
map l goForward
map H previousTab
map L nextTab
map <a-h> previousTab
map <a-l> nextTab
map J scrollDown
map K scrollUp
map j scrollPageDown
map k scrollPageUp
map s LinkHints.activateMode
map S LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map f LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
" capital i here:
map I LinkHints.activateModeToOpenIncognito
map zh scrollLeft
map zl scrollRight
map ' Marks.activateGotoMode

map 9 firstTab
map 0 lastTab
